    "description": "Climb to the sky while collecting countless stars.<br />\r\nNumerous gimmicks will try to knock you down without mercy,<br />\r\nBut if you keep going and don't give up, you will reach the top someday.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n■Game Features<br />\r\nThe game is a game of climbing up while collecting stars scattered in the field.<br />\r\nYou can save and stop the game at the starting point and at several other magic circles.<br />\r\nThe higher difficulty mode will be opened after the game is cleared.<br />\r\nAdditional costumes will be added after the game is cleared depending on the stars obtained (16 costumes in total, including the initial ones).<br />\r\nThe availability of gold stars will be reset after clearing the game, but the availability of stars of different colors will continue.<br />\r\n　(If you have already obtained them, they will be placed on the field in a semi-transparent state.)",
